A haunting fantasy portrait of a young woman standing amid a surreal garden of giant dandelions. Her expression is chillingly calm, her skin ghostly pale beneath tangled, platinum hair tied into high pigtails. She wears tattered rabbit ears and a baroque, gothic-style dress — layered with belts, lace, and weathered fabric stained in crimson and ash tones. The bodice is detailed with buckles and ornate stitching, giving the sense of a handcrafted relic from another world. Around her, white dandelion orbs tower at shoulder height, their delicate filaments drifting in the air alongside falling red rose petals. The atmosphere is dense, muted, and dreamlike, lit by a cold gray glow that blurs the line between innocence and menace. The composition evokes the aesthetic of dark fairytales, gothic horror, and steampunk surrealism, frozen in a moment that feels both tender and terrifying.
